00:15:10,570 --> 00:15:11,690
Jangan begitu, dong!

246
00:15:11,690 --> 00:15:14,400
Kau tak perlu ikut campur!

247
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:16,150
Pokoknya, kau pulang saja.

248
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:17,490
Ayo, Marie.

249
00:15:17,490 --> 00:15:20,620
Kakak, Asta,
