254
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:32,550
Ma...
Ma... Ma...

255
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:35,550
Orang aneh.

256
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:40,390
Sampai dia sadarkan diri, bagaimana
kalau kau makan malam di rumahku?

257
00:15:40,970 --> 00:15:43,850
Kalau kau mau,
kau juga boleh menginap.

258
00:15:43,850 --> 00:15:45,100
Boleh, nih?

259
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:45,890
Ya!

260
