312
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,970
Real Double.

313
00:19:54,390 --> 00:19:56,310
Sekarang ada dua kak Gauche?

314
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:58,140
Pertama dia tembakkan sinar
